g','1','1- مهديء قوي للكحة الجافة.','','6222006503437','',12372,'2024-06-27',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,NULL,'R05DB21',NULL),(32120,'Tadatrona 20 mg 4 f.c. tabs.','تاداترونا 20مجم 4 اقراص','100','','Tonic for men','Tadalafil','Averroes pharma','Tab','أقراص','20 mg','1','مقوى للرجال','','','',9099,'2023-04-23',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'Tadalafil is a selective phosphodiesterase-5 inhibitor that is used in the treatment of erectile dysfunction (ED), pulmonary arterial hypertension (PAH), and benign prostatic hypertrophy.[L39100, L39105] It was first approved in 2003 by the FDA for use in ED and later in 2009 for PAH. In contrast to other PDE5 inhibitors like [sildenafil], tadalafil has greater selectivity for PDE5 and a longer half-life which has made it a more suitable option for chronic once-daily dosing in the treatment of PAH.[A242287]','["G04BE08", "C02KX52", "G04CA54"]','[]'),(32121,'Sildatrona 100 mg 12 f.c.tabs.','سيلداترونا 100مجم 12 قرص','54','','Tonic for men','Sildenafil','Averroes pharma','Tab','أقراص','100 mg','3','مقوى للرجال','','6224008179900','',3091,'2023-04-23',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'In eliciting its mechanism of action, sildenafil ultimately prevents or minimizes the breakdown of cyclic guanosine monophosphate (cGMP) by inhibiting cGMP specific phosphodiesterase type 5 (PDE5) [F3850, F3853, F3856, F3859, F3883, F3886, L5611, L5614]. The result of doing so allows cGMP present in both the penis and pulmonary vasculature to elicit smooth muscle relaxation and vasodilation that subsequently facilitates relief in pulmonary arterial hypertension and the increased flow of blood into the spongy erectile tissue of the penis that consequently allows it to grow in size and become erect and rigid [F3850, F3853, F3856, F3859, F3883, F3886, L5611, L5614].

