oth muscle cells of the corpus cavernosum. The cGMP in turn triggers smooth muscle relaxation, allowing increased blood flow into the penis, resulting in erection. The tissue concentration of cGMP is regulated by both the rates of synthesis and degradation via phosphodiesterases (PDEs). The most abundant PDE in the human corpus cavernosum is the cGMPspecific phosphodiesterase type 5 (PDE5); therefore, the inhibition of PDE5 enhances erectile function by increasing the amount of cGMP.','["G04BE09"]','[]'),(32237,'Aaa','ششش','26','','','','','Unknown','غير محدد','','1','','','','',550,'2023-04-23',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(32238,'Aaa','ششش','8','','','','','Unknown','غير محدد','','3','','','','',546,'2023-04-23',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(32240,'Aaa','ششش','26','','','','','Unknown','غير محدد','','0','','','','',760,'2023-04-23',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(32242,'Aaa','ششش','188','','','','','Unknown','غير محدد','','1','','','','',742,'2023-04-23',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(32243,'Plasbumin 20% i.v. inf. vial 50 ml','بلازبيومين 20% للتسريب الوريدي 50 مل','1,450','962','Hypoalbuminemia','Human albumin','Grifols biological inc.-usa > biolinx medical inc.','Vial','فيال','20%','1','','','','',580,'2025-04-11',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,NULL,'B05AA01',NULL),(32244,'Actimo 100 mg 14 sachets','اكتيمو 100مجم 14 كيس','140','125','Iron supplement','Lactoferrin','> levana','Sachet','أكياس','100 mg','1','','','6225000486683','',1556,'2024-05-26',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(32245,'Potassium chloride 15% (mottahedoon) i.v. amp. 5 ml','بوتاسيوم كلورايد 15% المتحدون امبول وريدي 5 مل','4','2.5','Potassium supplement','Potassium chloride','Al mottahedoon pharma','Amp','أمبول','15%','1','','','','',991,'2025-08-08',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'Calcium chloride is an ionic compound of calcium and chlorine. It is highly soluble in water and it is deliquescent. It is a salt that is solid at room tempe